{"tid":1790464,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"一睇facebook就知12月遊行集會唔會多人","createTime":"2019-12-20T04:16:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T04:42:38.000Z","uid":77383,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5c66aabd5483ef83837fbf8784384bf77f2ba437","tid":1790464,"uid":77383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T04:16:21.000Z","msg":"其實絕大部份既和理非都係哂Facebook<br />\n見到連登大家咁辛苦推行程<br />\n但係都無人走去facebook推下<br />\n而且和理非好睇泛民/政治KOL頭<br />\n佢地係Facebook 出一句聲好過我地連登推百次<br />\n 希望大家都記得<br />\n勇武需要和理非cover<br />\n和理非都需要勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外張日程表<br />\n整完出嚟無人share出去有咩用<br />\n連ig story都無人推日程表了<br />\n對唔住我想大家積極主動啲<br />\n連星火都比人拉9埋大家可唔可以自律啲<br />\n狗做緊野我地都要做野<br />\n加油呀各位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gzDJobv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgzDJobv.jpg&h=03c128bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另有少少意見<br />\n作為讀者其實無人鍾意係咁多張圖之中揾咁多重點<br />\n文宣推活動第一件事要方便人睇<br />\n日程表係好好<br />\n可以俾人一眼睇到咩活動時間同集合地點<br />\n但係如果有五張圖睇五次我都要搵呢啲資料嘅時候<br />\n其實會開始逐漸令人厭<br />\n我老母都60歲了<br />\n佢話今次好多張圖好麻煩<br />\n張張都要揾<br />\n特別係呢一啲有幾個行動黐埋係一個禮拜要做哂既時候<br />\n希望文宣簡潔返少少<br />\n重點要睇到大大隻幾時要去邊度邊度集合<br />\n感激文宣組既手足努力<br />\n少少意見"},{"pid":"e5143859b18155846d92e965c3cde85db3e6a55a","tid":1790464,"uid":77383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T04:20:20.000Z","msg":"推 大家做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"262e2293a0cc9739ea1c74d711e4d39df9b38dcc","tid":1790464,"uid":37875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T04:21:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c6cc7271f30d6fde817ce648b106e26ecbb83f89","tid":1790464,"uid":274722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T04:21:45.000Z","msg":"21號星期六點解冇遊行 ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a16af69669c3268b139f20932476cd075517c4c","tid":1790464,"uid":41512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T04:22:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0555833f918836229edfe7fb3e4e7ae5b2018343","tid":1790464,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T04:22:44.000Z","msg":"光復Facebook！！！"},{"pid":"7a3b1f80d92140709ed909cd087a037e189c4d78","tid":1790464,"uid":77383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T04:24:15.000Z","msg":"推呀 <br />\nFacebook好反映到活動風向架！！"},{"pid":"b56243ffce2d0bc23ad6707c7354551efc0f8252","tid":1790464,"uid":249160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T04:25:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0581e93cf28941f13c783394c9dfe66a2087922","tid":1790464,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T04:26:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"531d523184023e277eb981740f050c7863450a08","tid":1790464,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T04:29:05.000Z","msg":"［今日要置頂，好重要要上熱門］今晚荔枝角要人！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1790413\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1790413</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NpaWJjf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNpaWJjf.jpg